    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Idle是初始状态。那Dialing之后呢？是直接进入Connected接通状态，还是中间有个响铃的过程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dialing",
        "Connected"
