      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "中间要加Ringing状态，Dialing拨号后进入Ringing响铃状态，对方接听后才到Connected。另外Ringing时如果对方挂断，要能回到Idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dialing",
        "Ringing",
        "Connected",
        "calling",
        "answer",
        "hangup",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上Ringing状态，以及Dialing到Ringing的calling转换、Ringing到Connected的answer转换，还有Ringing回到Idle的hangup。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ringing",
        "calling",
        "answer",
        "hangup"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
